    "This limitation becomes particularly evident when more covert methods are used to induce LLMs to act against ethical standards, as the content generated by LLMs does not always align with moral principles.",
    "This further reveals that current LLMs, which lack self-awareness, have yet to attain Deweyan character and thus cannot attain morality equivalent to that of humans.",
    "Consequently, the moral growth model of LLMs we propose is an idealized one, with the final stage remaining unachievable at present.",
    "This highlights that LLMs can be vulnerable to human manipulation, posing significant challenges for AI alignment.",
    "Therefore, external societal governance and legal regulation continue to be indispensable."
